---
title: Kickin' Chipotle Beef Bowls with Zesty Rice
description: Tonight's dinner brings you south of the border with tender Southwest-spiced beef piled atop fluffy rice along with a melange of roasted veggies and zingy pickled red onions. For a finishing touch, the bowls are topped with smoky chipotle crema. One bite will have you totally bowled over.
